02:32.782 --> 02:33.914
Thanks, Christmas tree.

02:33.950 --> 02:37.385
Oh, we love you, Christmas tree.

02:39.088 --> 02:40.088
Morning, gorgeous.

02:40.123 --> 02:41.255
Hey, where we going?

02:41.291 --> 02:46.628
Oh, um, we're all going on
vacation to universal studios.

02:46.663 --> 02:48.396
Awesome!

02:48.465 --> 02:51.299
I want to go to Harry Potter land
and try that fake butterbeer.

02:51.334 --> 02:52.467
You're grabbing the luggage?

02:52.503 --> 02:54.302
Remember, grab the sunscreen.

02:54.338 --> 02:55.303
[ Garbage truck beeping ]

02:55.372 --> 02:56.104
Hold up, there.

02:56.139 --> 02:56.771
No, no, no.

02:56.840 --> 02:59.474
I'm actually about to head
to Florida with my family.

02:59.509 --> 03:00.942
Carol! Help!

03:01.010 --> 03:02.810
Jeff, get out here, man!

03:02.845 --> 03:04.045
They think I'm trash!

03:04.113 --> 03:06.213
I thought I was part of the family.

03:06.282 --> 03:09.850
You lied to me, you bastards!

03:09.918 --> 03:11.852
Are you [bleep] kidding me?!

03:13.154 --> 03:14.054
Think positive.

03:14.123 --> 03:17.224
Maybe someone will just use
me for boogers or number one.

03:17.259 --> 03:18.325
Wait a minute.

03:18.360 --> 03:19.392
Is this <i>them?</i>

03:19.427 --> 03:21.394
<i>Sally, get some extra
toilet paper, okay, hon?</i>

03:21.430 --> 03:22.829
<i>We're having Indian food tonight.</i>

03:22.864 --> 03:23.663
<i>[ Laughs ]</i>

03:23.699 --> 03:25.232
<i>Oh, no, no, no!</i>

03:25.267 --> 03:27.735
<i>Dear, we thought we could use
this after your chimney accident.</i>

03:27.770 --> 03:28.869
<i>Ho! Ho! Ho!</i>

03:28.905 --> 03:31.105
<i>A candy cane -- how thoughtful.</i>

03:31.140 --> 03:31.505
<i>Aah!</i>

03:31.540 --> 03:32.139
<i>Oh, no.</i>

03:32.208 --> 03:33.974
It was actually <i>made</i> of candy?

03:34.043 --> 03:35.509
We thought it would hold you!

03:35.545 --> 03:37.512
Oh, was this load-bearing peppermint?

03:37.580 --> 03:38.046
Oh, God.

03:38.114 --> 03:40.682
I shattered my tibia.

03:40.751 --> 03:42.517
Aw, that's not fair!

03:42.586 --> 03:45.320
Who's laughing at "Big Foot" Danny now.

03:45.355 --> 03:50.024
Welcome back to "The Justin Bieber
Christmas Special With Love."

03:50.060 --> 03:51.226
I love you all.

03:51.261 --> 03:56.898
This is a song I wrote about Christmas
and how it makes my heart feel.

03:56.966 --> 03:58.365
[ Heavy-metal music plays ]

03:58.434 --> 04:00.968
