07:20.975 --> 07:22.307
[ Laughs ]

07:22.376 --> 07:23.742
[ Smooches ]

07:23.777 --> 07:25.443
Oh, boy! Oh, boy! Oh, boy!

07:25.479 --> 07:27.379
Christmas! Yay!

07:27.414 --> 07:31.116
♪ Jingle bells, mom's in
tears, what is going on? ♪

07:31.151 --> 07:32.584
Everybody, be cool.

07:32.653 --> 07:34.186
We've just been robbed!

07:34.221 --> 07:36.188
Bastards even took the tree.

07:36.223 --> 07:39.591
What could the black-market
value on a rapidly-browning

07:39.626 --> 07:41.126
Douglas fir possibly be?

07:41.161 --> 07:42.861
No -- no presents?

07:42.930 --> 07:45.130
Oh, honey, it's totally fine.

07:45.199 --> 07:48.234
