09:54.230 --> 09:55.095
Hey, hey, hey.

09:55.164 --> 09:56.297
Let's not get personal.

09:56.332 --> 09:57.198
You know what?

09:57.233 --> 09:57.998
Keep my stuff.

09:58.034 --> 10:01.669
I'm about to give myself the best
Christmas present of all time.

10:01.704 --> 10:03.304
Nooooooo!

10:03.372 --> 10:05.539
[ Whistle! ]

10:05.574 --> 10:06.006
[ Crash! ]

10:06.042 --> 10:09.943
Merry Christmas to all, and
to all, a good -- [ Barking ]

10:09.978 --> 10:10.844
Oh, my gosh.

10:10.912 --> 10:13.113
That little Stockholm-syndrome dog.

10:13.181 --> 10:14.113
